A better way to do it would be something like:

; Create shape with desired width, height and depth
InitShape shp_num,shp_width,shp_height,shp_depth

; Use shape data as a bitmap
ShapesBitMap shp_num,bmp_num

BltBitMap_ *guigfx_bm,0,0,Addr
BitMap(bmp_num),0,0,shp_width,shp_height,$C0,-1,0

But both your GuiGFX bitmap and shape should be the same size.

